{"tid":517032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾300荷里活女星及導演等發起「Time's Up」計劃　打擊性騷擾行為","createTime":"2018-01-02T02:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T04:32:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6799cd644861c14183e094eabc7ed4e1a0e89ca9","tid":517032,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1372899_1_20180102093514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1372899_1_20180102093514.jpg&h=cd8964fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超過300名荷里活女演員、編劇及導演發起計劃，打擊在演藝界及其他界別的性騷擾行為。<br />\n<br />\n他們在《紐約時報》刊登全版廣告，宣布計劃，表示要團結發聲，為演藝界及其他地方的女性帶來改變。<br />\n<br />\n支持計劃的包括奧斯卡影后愛瑪史東及妮坦莉寶雯等，計劃期望為職場性騷擾行為的受害人，不論男女，提供法律訴訟的經費。協助目標包括財政能力較低人士，例如工廠女工及女侍應等。<br />\n<br />\n計劃目標籌募1500萬美元作為基金，現時已籌得大約1300萬美元。"},{"pid":"b2314c3e7831dab1b82895a6bb74fa9dba3c163a","tid":517032,"uid":62599,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:39:32.000Z","msg":"#METOO大聯盟"},{"pid":"415763b2e715ec993d43424107404bd8ca4ce793","tid":517032,"uid":36010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"妖妖：#timesup #metoo"},{"pid":"6fdf856bf8bbf61d42d7a8c1c88da2d7927abed9","tid":517032,"uid":59898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 繼續搞臭女權個名"},{"pid":"1e1fc00d520b1cbd558aea99acc9a112237830f1","tid":517032,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"415763b2e715ec993d43424107404bd8ca4ce793","tid":517032,"uid":36010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:39:39